    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay, i'll try the tylenol instead then. but wait, i actually have some extra naproxen in my cabinet from before. is that any different or is it the same thing? if the ibuprofen is too risky, maybe the naproxen is a safer bet for a quick headache fix?",
